title: SpaceX launches 1st Starlink satellites of 2026 on new Falcon 9 rocket (video)
description: A SpaceX Falcon 9 rocket carrying 29 Starlink satellites launched from Cape Canaveral Space Force Station in Florida on Sunday, Jan. 4, 2026.
